Find the job from the the link https://socialclub.rockstargames.com/jobs
Then book mark the job and reload the game!
1. Download the two files>
2. Open GTA go to online session
3. Menu>Online>Jobs>Play job>Bookmarks> Survival> Then select the name of the job
4. Play the job
5. After the confirmations and settings changes when the job stars to load 
6. Run the Afk_Money_RP_V2 file on any editor
7. Switch to the GTA window
8. And go watch a Netflix show :)
9. It will score RPs and Money
10. Enjoy the game without grinding :)

Note: Only workable on PC console
